                "12": {
                  "id": "12",
                  "speaker": "Halsin",
                  "text": "Sometimes it is difficult to see exactly what we are fighting to save here. Sometimes the Shadow Druids' desire to separate nature from all this seems pragmatic, not fanatical...",
